{"id": 2229, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得，哪些“善意的谎言”其实挺讨厌的？", "description": "就，不要再用“白色谎言”来包装欺骗和不真诚了。", "record_count": 3126, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180316101558Yi4LsV8MRo9nfSeZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-16T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 270848, "content": "老婆，今年去我家，明年去你家过年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287065}, {"id": 270849, "content": "说是为了我好 其实都只是让自己体面和少点麻烦而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274079}, {"id": 270850, "content": "出轨了不说，怕对方知道了难过，你可以炸了", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529895}, {"id": 271106, "content": "对不起，你想要的我给不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204189}, {"id": 270851, "content": "无聊\n这两个字只是代表想找你说说话而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287071}, {"id": 271107, "content": "总是说着很忙 却偷偷去打游戏 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289310}, {"id": 270853, "content": "你已经很好了，你不要想多了，我是为你好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287082}, {"id": 270854, "content": "“呵呵。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775953}, {"id": 270855, "content": "“都是为你好。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283802}, {"id": 271113, "content": "应该坦诚啊，我很不喜欢被欺骗，任何谎言我都无法接受，除了开玩笑?️", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1241317}, {"id": 270859, "content": "everything will be OK", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 877673}, {"id": 270861, "content": "下次约", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287112}, {"id": 270862, "content": "明明想吃，就说自己不饿", "image": "img/option/option/20180316142432OHbxoqm9QVu0zXDW.jpg", "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287122}, {"id": 270863, "content": "明明生活过的一塌糊涂，爸妈问起来时还说过的很好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287124}, {"id": 271119, "content": "下次再约。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285966}, {"id": 270864, "content": "被讨厌的就不能算作善意的谎言了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286404}, {"id": 270865, "content": "公司明年上市", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792255}, {"id": 270866, "content": "你并不丑，你很可爱啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265080}, {"id": 271122, "content": "明明互相喜欢，却都说不喜欢对方，总怕对方喜欢的人不是自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1067405}, {"id": 270867, "content": "其实你挺好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223270}, {"id": 270869, "content": "你决定吧，我都可以", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287157}, {"id": 274197, "content": "你很棒，下次你一定能做得更好\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303811}, {"id": 271382, "content": "爸爸不要你了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290328}, {"id": 277271, "content": "其实你很聪明，就是不学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275677}, {"id": 271129, "content": "全错了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289626}, {"id": 270874, "content": "我还是很爱你的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205726}, {"id": 270875, "content": "加油！你可以的！\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260098}, {"id": 271131, "content": "你很好，只是时间是毒药，我们饮尽此杯，并发誓永不再相爱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289690}, {"id": 270876, "content": "还可以做朋友吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941979}, {"id": 270877, "content": "我这都是为你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285337}, {"id": 271645, "content": "我是一个大傻子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291139}, {"id": 270879, "content": "和多个异性搞暧昧说是纯友谊……醉了", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154864}, {"id": 270880, "content": "把低级无聊的牛逼吹得高大上", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287213}, {"id": 272416, "content": "考上大学就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293814}, {"id": 270881, "content": "我先去冲凉，等下再聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287218}, {"id": 270882, "content": "我怕你多想，所以才最后告诉你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282627}, {"id": 270883, "content": "呃。。你说的也对", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279003}, {"id": 270884, "content": "加了班给你们发奖金啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287245}, {"id": 270886, "content": "其实你是个好人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287292}, {"id": 270888, "content": "过两天就还钱给你", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286974}, {"id": 275753, "content": "站在道德至高点的为你着想", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315324}, {"id": 270890, "content": "说很喜欢舍不得走却是离开得最快的\n\"我会等你的\"事实上根本没有谁会等谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1170501}, {"id": 270891, "content": "嗯...这堂课让大家先自学我再讲是为了提起大家的兴趣~", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287317}, {"id": 270892, "content": "老师巴拉巴拉布置一堆作业  最后来一句  大家不要哭啊  (加一个抱抱的表情)", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287317}, {"id": 270894, "content": "借着忠言逆耳的名义来打击你。还说那些鼓励你的人是虚情假意。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286652}, {"id": 270895, "content": "好好干，涨工资", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589587}, {"id": 270896, "content": "我相信你", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287328}, {"id": 270897, "content": "我没打你小报告。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282989}, {"id": 270898, "content": "约了吃饭 明明还有好久才能到  却总是说很快就到了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280351}, {"id": 270643, "content": "爸妈还是把我当小孩子，家里有人生病或有什么事都是自己解决差不多了才告诉我", "image": null, "praise_count": 473, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}]}